description:
bughz: they travel through light and thought. Glitch as freedom. Sergio Aguirrre creates these compositions by manipulating his hands to imitate an alien hand that moves by itself, but with a peculiarly Mexican texture that is completely unrecognizable in reality. His art comes from the natural contours of very heavy notes that vibrate together like jellyfish, at least once or twice before disappearing into nothingness (as if no sound is coming out).
